body.p:
To style the highlighted text from the document content, use the
        oxy-comment-hl element (or oxy-delete-hl,
        oxy-insert-hl, respectively, by local name or class
      name):oxy-comment-hl,
.oxy-comment-hl {
  color:magenta;
}

body.codeblock:
oxy-range-start:before,
.oxy-range-start:before {
  display:inline;
  content:'[' attr(hr_id) ']';
  color:red;
}
oxy-range-end:before,
.oxy-range-end:before {
  display:inline;
  content:'[/' attr(hr_id) ']';
  color:red;
}
